"<span style=\"color: rgb(55, 65, 81); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; "
"font-weight: 400;\" class=\"bg-o-color-4\">\n"
"                                                <font class=\"bg-o-"
"color-3\">Elevate your brand and revenue with our sales and marketing "
"professionals.</font>\n"
"                                            </span>\n"
"                                            <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"color: rgb(55, 65, 81); font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; "
"font-weight: 400;\" class=\"bg-o-color-4\">\n"
"                                                <font class=\"bg-o-color-3\">"
"영업 및 마케팅 전문가의 도움을 받아 브랜드와 수익을 높이세요.</font>\n"
"                                            </span>\n"
"                                            <br/>"

#. module: headhunter
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:headhunter.homepage
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400;\" "
"class=\"bg-o-color-2 text-o-color-3\">Our financial experts can help you "
"find top-notch finance and accounting professionals.</span>\n"
